  "After Sales ECM PAIRING": {
   "width": 9660,
   "height": 10020,
   "color": "rgb(0,0,255)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "AFTER SALES ECM pairing  ",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,0)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 120,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 9360
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Pairing procedure : ",
     "color": "rgb(128,128,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 135,
      "top": 600,
      "height": 3360,
      "width": 9360
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Complete the \"After Sales Code\" (16 bytes) and press the button \"ENTER ECM AFTER SALES MODE\"",
     "color": "rgb(128,128,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 1680,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 9120
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Parts Pairing information",
     "color": "rgb(128,128,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 7200,
      "height": 2760,
      "width": 3960
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Pairing Mode Information",
     "color": "rgb(128,128,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 4080,
      "height": 3000,
      "width": 9360
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) If the authorization to pair the ECM is OK, put Ignition ON. Once the ECM is paired, the exit of the ECM AFTER SALES MODE is automatic",
     "color": "rgb(128,128,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 2520,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 9120
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Authentication information",
     "color": "rgb(128,128,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 4200,
      "top": 7200,
      "height": 2760,
      "width": 5280
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) Put Ignition ON and check that the ECM is blank",
     "color": "rgb(128,128,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 840,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 8040
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) Put Ignition OFF",
     "color": "rgb(128,128,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 1440,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 2880
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "To Cancel the authorization to pair the ECM, press the button \"EXIT ECM AFTER SALES PAIRING\"",
     "color": "rgb(128,128,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 3120,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 9120
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    }
   ],
